    "asOf": "2011-06-22",
    "date": "2011-08-11T16:37:43Z",
    "text": "Post-deployment Strategy Act of 2011 - Amends the War Powers Resolution to direct the President to include a post-deployment strategy in the required report to Congress when introducing U.S. Armed Forces into hostilities and certain other situations without a declaration of war.\n\nDefines \"post-deployment strategy\" as a clear action plan that: (1) articulates U.S. interests, (2) defines and lays out a strategy for achieving policy objectives, and (3) includes a withdrawal plan based on such objectives."
  },
